    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-9004499f-d83c-4196-b6e6-e9f4d661c401">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-9004499f-d83c-4196-b6e6-e9f4d661c401">
                Mr. Shinwell
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-9004499f-d83c-4196-b6e6-e9f4d661c401" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-06-13/debates/c3e531a4-82b4-48b4-a184-78bc2a9b51b1/280Rifle#contribution-9004499f-d83c-4196-b6e6-e9f4d661c401">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The question is now under consideration by the various Commonwealth Governments.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-9004499f-d83c-4196-b6e6-e9f4d661c401" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-06-13/debates/c3e531a4-82b4-48b4-a184-78bc2a9b51b1/280Rifle#contribution-9004499f-d83c-4196-b6e6-e9f4d661c401">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-976159d3-e37b-4701-9bd6-0716d6546ae2">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-976159d3-e37b-4701-9bd6-0716d6546ae2">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-976159d3-e37b-4701-9bd6-0716d6546ae2">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-976159d3-e37b-4701-9bd6-0716d6546ae2">
                Brigadier Head
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-976159d3-e37b-4701-9bd6-0716d6546ae2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-06-13/debates/c3e531a4-82b4-48b4-a184-78bc2a9b51b1/280Rifle#contribution-976159d3-e37b-4701-9bd6-0716d6546ae2">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is it not already a fact that the Dominion of Canada is retaining the same calibre as the United States? Will not this have a most unfortunate effect on unity in Imperial defence, and does it not mean that, in future, Canadian formations will have to fight shoulder to shoulder with American rather than British formations?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-976159d3-e37b-4701-9bd6-0716d6546ae2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-06-13/debates/c3e531a4-82b4-48b4-a184-78bc2a9b51b1/280Rifle#contribution-976159d3-e37b-4701-9bd6-0716d6546ae2">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-ed2a9de5-75bb-4868-be7b-df81f0ef9729">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-ed2a9de5-75bb-4868-be7b-df81f0ef9729">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-ed2a9de5-75bb-4868-be7b-df81f0ef9729">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-ed2a9de5-75bb-4868-be7b-df81f0ef9729">
                Mr. Shinwell
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-ed2a9de5-75bb-4868-be7b-df81f0ef9729" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-06-13/debates/c3e531a4-82b4-48b4-a184-78bc2a9b51b1/280Rifle#contribution-ed2a9de5-75bb-4868-be7b-df81f0ef9729">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">It may be regarded as regrettable that Canada has decided to adopt the United States weapon, which, of course, has been in existence for a long time, but I hardly think it can be said that this will disrupt unity in Imperial defence.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-ed2a9de5-75bb-4868-be7b-df81f0ef9729" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-06-13/debates/c3e531a4-82b4-48b4-a184-78bc2a9b51b1/280Rifle#contribution-ed2a9de5-75bb-4868-be7b-df81f0ef9729">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-abf744e0-70a2-4fc8-9e15-627eb392b736">
